text: Him is an upcoming American sports horror movie. It is expected to be released on September 19, 2025. It was first going to be titled GOAT before being changed. It was directed by Justin Tipping and produced by Jordan Peele, Win Rosenfeld, Ian Cooper, and Jamal Watson. The movie follows Cameron Cade, an rising prospect who is invited to train with a retiring star of a team.
